{
  "id": "10295",
  "key": "GG-292",
  "fields": {
    "summary": "[Backend] Real Time Progress Update of Migration Progress to Frontend",
    "description": {
      "type": "doc",
      "version": 1,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use case:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As a user overseeing a data migration, I want the backend to send real-time progress updates to the frontend so that I can monitor the migration's progress and see an accurate representation on the loading bar."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Acceptance criteria:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The backend must stream real-time migration progress updates to the frontend."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The progress updates must include detailed status information such as percentage completed and any relevant messages or errors."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The updates must be delivered at regular intervals to ensure smooth real-time tracking."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The backend must handle any errors or interruptions in the migration process and send appropriate notifications to the frontend."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The system must ensure data consistency and integrity during the migration process."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Technical notes:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Implement the progress update mechanism using either WebSocket connections or polling to push updates to the frontend."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If using WebSockets: Establish a WebSocket server to send real-time updates to connected clients."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If using polling: Implement an API endpoint that clients can call at regular intervals to fetch the latest progress updates."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Ensure the progress updates include necessary information such as migration status, percentage completed, and error messages (if any)."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Implement error handling and recovery mechanisms to ensure reliable updates in case of network or system failures."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Optimize the backend service for performance to minimize latency and ensure timely delivery of progress updates."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Ensure the progress update mechanism is scalable to handle multiple concurrent migrations and clients."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
